Twitcurses - A ncurses based Twitter client.
---

Features:
 * Update your account
 * Refresh the timeline
 * On Mac speaks your newest tweet using say command.

Move the dot.twitcurses to $HOME/.twitcurses and add your twitter username and password to the file.
Note: refresh-rate is in seconds

Commands:
ESC - refresh timeline
Q - quit
T - new tweet
M - mute (on Mac this prevents the say command from invoking)
U - Show user tweets

Requirements:
gem install twitter
